name: Back to Route 8O8
description:
Big Frank a.k.a The Robot, the member of Alley Katz, coming back to Route 8O8 from the last heist with some random guys from Distort Area. He's doing this job because of poverty that strike Route 8O8 from 3 years ago.

Public transportation, such as train, is very safe transportation in Main City. Main City Polize wouldn't check it, because in Main City only poor people who still using public transportation. So, many gang or graffiti bomber loves to hit with train & other public transportation.

Big Frank said it'll be his last heist with some random guys. He will doing a bigger heist with his childhood friends who known as Alley Katz from Route 8O8.

What kind of action they will do? We will see it as soon as possible.
